    <div class="contentPane">
        <section class="l-page-block l-text-block">
            <div class="l-content-container container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col">
                        <h1>
More about the INTO The University of Alabama at Birmingham Center                        </h1>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col">
                        <p>When you study here you'll enjoy all the benefits of campus life at an American university. Living and learning in the heart of the University of Alabama at Birmingham campus, you'll meet new friends among both American and international students. You'll also have access to all of the academic, social and cultural resources and activities at UAB.</p>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="l-detailed-info l-page-block block-bottom-spacer">
            <div class="l-content-container">
                <section>
                    

    <div class="l-accordian-container">
        <a class="accordian-control">
            Learning facilities
            <span>
                <em></em>
            </span>
        </a>

        <div class="l-accordian">
            <div>
                <p>You'll enjoy access to all campus facilities and learning resources, including the University Academic Success Center. Our center promotes and fosters student success, enhances academic performance and inspires you to achieve your academic, professional and personal goals. The INTO UAB resources are intentionally designed to facilitate experiences that encourage your persistence and prepares you for life after graduation.</p>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="l-accordian-container">
            <a class="accordian-control">
                Learning Resource Center
                <span>
                    <em></em>
                </span>
            </a>
            <div class="l-accordian">
                <div>
                    <p>The INTO UAB Learning Resource Center is a vital part of your experience. Your success is essential. We provide access to tutoring services, writing resources and mentoring sessions to help you achieve that success.</p>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="l-accordian-container">
            <a class="accordian-control">
                Student Life
                <span>
                    <em></em>
                </span>
            </a>
            <div class="l-accordian">
                <div>
                    <h3>Student Services</h3>
<p>All students of INTO UAB Academic English and Pathways programs have access to a variety of activities and events offered by INTO UAB. Students also have access to all organizations, activities, and events available to them as UAB students.
We provide the following:</p>
<ul>
<li>Orientation program</li>
<li>International mentors program</li>
<li>Language advisors</li>
<li>Visa and immigration support</li>
<li>Learning Resource Center</li>
<li>Language Partners</li>
<li>Language Exchange</li>
<li>Friendship Partners program</li>
<li>Trips and activities</li>
</ul>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

                    

